<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-100">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mdb-ui-kit/1.0.0/mdb.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/css/main.css">
    <meta name="og:site_name" content="한번 등록으로 매일 자동 자가진단">
    <meta property="og:title" content="E-Z 자동 자가진단">
    <meta property="og:description" content="By Tritium Networks">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#4C566A">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://hcs.trinets.xyz/src/img/secondary_pw_bg.jpg">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
    <title>ez 자동 자가진단</title>
  </head>
  <body class="w-100 h-100 background">
    <div class="container foreground w-100 shadow p-0">
      <div class="text-center jumbotron p-5 text-white shadow">
        <h1>E-Z 자동 자가진단</h1>
        <h5>한번 등록으로 매일 자동 자가진단</h5>
      </div>

      <div class="container mt-5 p-5">
        <form method="POST" action="/api/disapply">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
              <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                <input required type="text" name="studentName" id="studentName" class="form-control text-white" />
                <label class="form-label text-white" for="studentName">학생명</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6">
              <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                <input required type="number" min=10101 name="birth" id="birth" class="form-control text-white" />
                <label class="form-label text-white" for="birth">생년월일 (6자)</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12">
              <div class="form-outline mb-4">
                <input required type="tel" name="password" maxlength="4" id="password" class="form-control text-white" />
                <label class="form-label text-white" for="password">비밀번호 (4자)</label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-nord text-white mb-4 mr-2" type="submit" value="checked">탈퇴</button>
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-danger text-white mb-4">돌아가기</a>
          <p class="text-white">비밀번호를 분실하신 경우 <a href="mailto:pmhstudio.pmh@gmail.com">여기</a>로 이메일을 보내주시면 확인후 탈퇴해 드립니다.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-2 text-center text-white">
      <button type="button" class=" btn btn-nord btn-sm text-white mr-1" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#credit">
        Credits
      </button>
      Hosted with <span style="color: #e25555;">&hearts;</span> by <a class="hover-shadow" href="https://trinets.xyz" style="color: #6bedd4">Tritium Networks</a>.
    </div>

    <div
      class="modal fade"
      id="credit"
      tabindex="-1"
      aria-labelledby="creditLabel"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header text-white bg-dark">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="creditLabel">만든이들 & 도움준 사람들</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body bg-dark text-white text-center">
            백엔드 및 UI디자인 (2차)<br />
            PMH, Park Min Hyeok (<a href="https://github.com/pmh-only" class="fg-nord">Github</a>/<a href="mailto:pmhstudio.pmh@gmail.com" class="fg-nord">Email</a>)<br /><br />

            API 및 통신 분석 (원작자)<br />
            comjun04<br /><br />

            보조 프로그래밍 및 테스터<br />
            Noeul<br /><br />

            투덜투덜 및 테스터<br />
            Teaddy<br /><br />

            and 트리튬섭 멤버들 (<a href="https://discord.gg/VbcGYnv" class="fg-nord">Discord</a>)
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mdb-ui-kit/1.0.0/mdb.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/src/js/disapply.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
